These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-1::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, bolivar
City: paris, berlin
The people have 2 different hobbies: board-games, chess
There are 2 different favourite colors: black, purple
1. the person who likes black is not to the right of the person traveling to berlin##8
2. the person traveling to berlin is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##5
3. the vegafina-smoker is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |
| Cigar      | bolivar     | vegafina      |
| City          | berlin | paris    |
| Hobby         | chess   | board-games |
| Color   | black  | purple      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, iced-tea
City: colone, liverpool
There 2 different types of food: apple, corn
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: zombie, drama
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far right##1
2. the person traveling to colone is somewhere to the left of the person eating apple##5
3. the person eating corn is not to the right of the person eating apple##8
4. the person watching zombie movies is not the person traveling to liverpool##6

.:: Answer ::.
|             |         1          |      2      |
| Beverage    | almond-milk        | iced-tea    |
| City       | colone         | liverpool |
| Food         | corn | apple   |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie               | drama  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-3::.
