There are 2 different favourite colors: apricot, brown
There are 2 different nationalities: australian, japanese
The people have 2 different jobs:  dancer, dressmaker
1. the australian is in an odd position##4
2. the japanese is not to the right of the dressmaker##8
3. the person who likes apricot is somewhere to the left of the dunhill-smoker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Cigar   | aristoff       | dunhill |
| Color   | apricot       | brown    |
| Nationality   | australian | japanese |
| Job           | dancer        | dressmaker   |

