City: edinburgh, london
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: mystery, spy
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: september, october
1. the person watching spy movies is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in september##8
2. the person watching spy movies is on the left or right of the fan of techno##3
3. the person who's birthday is in september is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |
| Music-Genre      | techno    | jazz   |
| City          | edinburgh   | london   |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | spy        |
| Birthday   | october | september |

