.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-15::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: bellflower, aconite
There are 2 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, water
There 2 different types of food: onion, pineapple
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: climbing, rowing
1. the person who growsaconite is not to the left of the person drinking soy-milk##8
2. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the person eating onion##3
3. the person eating onion is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is climbing##5
4. the person drinking soy-milk is not to the left of the person who growsaconite##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |
| Flower         | aconite  | bellflower  |
| Beverage           | soy-milk    | water |
| Food   | onion | pineapple  |
| Sport         | rowing  | climbing |

